div.div:
After being put on trial, the deity once known as "The Divine Twilight" is offered a job by Thanatos, king of the underworld! Now, the fallen deity is back on Earth as his former self, Lee Chang-Seon, and is tasked with sealing those trying to invade from beyond. With the promise of a fresh start, Chang-Seon is gathering the gear and skills needed to get the job done, but he's feeling some watchful eyes on him... Will this Divine Twilight see a new day, or is the sun setting on his second chance?
(Source: Tapas, edited)

“Who’s this male prostitute-looking kid?”
I am the matchless Ha Hu-Yeong, the greatest martial artist reigning over all the lands! There is no one that is my equal! I was drowning in futility and emptiness because there was no more that I could accomplish in the human realm. To reach the peak of martial arts, I must become a saint! However, the other saints refused my ascension due to my karma after much slaughter, and I fell, just like that.
When I woke up, I was 60 years in the future. I was reborn as the second lord of the Namgung family: Namgung Hyuk. Where has all the internal energy that I’ve accumulated gone?! Moreover, I have the Nine yin energy blockage?
(Source: Kakao, translated and edited)
